name: Splashter
description:
Makes the image "splashy", glass/paint/liquid like. Splashes will be a lot nicer. Works well with most of the models.

  • If the effect is too strong: either lower the weight of the embedding or use negative prompts to fix the problematic areas

  • If the effect is not strong enough: put more weight on the trigger word

Be careful with negative prompts because they can cancel out the effect!

If you want to create just beautiful splash images don't type any prompt BUT the "Slpashter_2" trigger word in the main 1.5 model.
